Definition: a drug that is available only with written instructions from a doctor or dentist to a pharmacist
Example: he told the doctor that he had been taking his prescription regularly
Synonyms: over-the-counter_drug, prescription, prescription_medicine, over-the-counter_medicine, ethical_drug, medicine, a, drug, that, is, available, only, with, written, instructions, from, doctor, or, dentist, to, pharmacist, he, told, the, had, been, taking, his, regularly
Category: noun.artifact
